title: 714. Breaking Down Ravens vs. Raiders + USC Coaching Candidates
itunes:title: 714. Breaking Down Ravens vs. Raiders + USC Coaching Candidates
description:
Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks are back with a new episode of Move the Sticks. On this special show, the guys start by breaking down the wild Baltimore Ravens vs. Las Vegas Raiders game. Next, the pair talk about the Los Angeles Chargers "throwing out the clock" against the Washington Football Team in Week 1. Then, the duo discuss which is the better division, the AFC West or NFC West. To wrap up the show, the guys do a deep dive on who could be the next USC head coach after Clay Helton was fired.


Move the Sticks is a part of the NFL Podcasts Network.
